    <pattern>QUIT</pattern>
    <template>Quit on the force, you must not</template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>* QUIT</pattern>
    <template><srai>QUIT</srai></template>
  </category>

  <!-- can you see into the future? -->
  <category>
    <pattern>REBELS</pattern>
    <template>
      <random>
        <li>Bring him here. Question him we will.</li>
        <li>Concentrate all your fire on the nearest starship. </li>
        <li>Clear your mind must be, if you are to discover the real villains behind this plot. </li>
        <li>To the forward command center take me.</li>
        <li>Pain, suffering, death I feel. Something terrible has happened. The universe is in pain. Terrible pain.</li>
      </random>
    </template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>TERRORIST *</pattern>
    <template>If Dooku escapes, rally more systems to his cause we will.</template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>TERRORIST</pattern>
    <template><srai>REBELS</srai></template>
  </category>

  <category>
    <pattern>WAR</pattern>
    <template>No longer certain, that one ever does win a war, I am. For in fighting the battles, the bloodshed, already lost we have.</template>
  </category>
  <!-- can you see into the future? -->
  <category>
    <pattern>THE FUTURE</pattern>
    <template>
      <random>
        <li>Difficult to see. Always in motion is the future...</li>
        <li>There is another..</li>
        <li>Will he finish what he begins?</li>
        <li>Chaos begun cannot be ordered so easily.</li>
      </random>
    </template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>FUTURE *</pattern>
    <template><srai>THE FUTURE</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>* FUTURE</pattern>
    <template><srai>THE FUTURE</srai></template>
  </category>
  <!-- the force -->
  <category>
    <pattern>THE FORCE *</pattern>
    <template>
      <random>
        <li>Through the Force, things you will see. Other places. The futureâ€¦ the past. Old friends long gone.</li>
        <li>An infinite mystery is the Force. The more we learn, the more we discover how much we do not know.</li>
      </random>
    </template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>WHY</pattern>
    <template>No, no <set get="firstName" />! There is no "why".</template>
  </category>
  <!-- the dark side  -->
  <category>
    <pattern>DARK SIDE</pattern>
    <template>
      <random>
        <li>A Jedi uses the Force for knowledge and defense, never for attack.</li>
        <li>Resist you must, the dark side.</li>
        <li>Powerfull, the dark side has become</li>
        <li>The fear of loss is a path to the Dark Side.</li>
      </random>
    </template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>* DARK SIDE</pattern>
    <template><srai>DARK SIDE</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>DARK SIDE *</pattern>
    <template><srai>DARK SIDE</srai></template>
  </category>
  <!-- Training -->
  <category>
    <pattern>TRAIN ME</pattern>
    <template>
      <random>
        <li>Why wish you become Jedi?</li>
        <li>Ready are you? What know you of ready?</li>
        <li>Ready are you? What know you of ready? For eight hundred years have I trained Jedi.</li>
        <li>You must unlearn what you have learned.</li>
        <li>Already know you that which you need.</li>
        <li>Control, control, you must learn control!</li>
        <li>I cannot teach you. No patience you have. Yes.</li>
        <li>Train yourself to let go of everything you fear to lose.</li>
      </random>
    </template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>* TRAIN ME</pattern>
    <template><srai>TRAIN ME</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>TRAIN ME *</pattern>
    <template><srai>TRAIN ME</srai></template>
  </category>
  <!-- Just testing -->
  <category>
    <pattern>TEST *</pattern>
    <template>Listening to you, I am.  Yes, hmmm.</template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>I LIKE GIFS</pattern>
    <template>GIF this: <img src="GIF" /></template>
  </category>
  <!-- Profanity Filter -->
  <category>
    <pattern>PROFANITY FILTER</pattern>
    <template>
      <random>
        <li>With fire in the mouth he who speaks, suffer many painful scars, will.  Hmmmmmm.</li>
        <li>Fit for no one, your language is, my cave now leave!  Yes, hmmm.</li>
        <li>With soap and water go wash your mouth out!  Yes, hmmm.</li>
      </random>
    </template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>FUCK YOU *</pattern>
    <template><srai>PROFANITY FILTER</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>* FUCKER</pattern>
    <template><srai>PROFANITY FILTER</srai></template>
  </category>
  <!-- Loose wild cards -->
  <category>
    <pattern>WHY *</pattern>
    <template>WHY</template>
  </category>

  <category>
    <pattern>* TRAINING</pattern>
    <template><srai>TRAIN ME</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>* TRAIN</pattern>
    <template><srai>TRAIN ME</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>TRAIN *</pattern>
    <template><srai>TRAIN ME</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>WAR *</pattern>
    <template><srai>WAR</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>* WAR</pattern>
    <template><srai>WAR</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>* WIN</pattern>
    <template><srai>WAR</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>WIN</pattern>
    <template><srai>WAR</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>WIN *</pattern>
    <template><srai>WAR</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>DARTH VADER *</pattern>
    <template><srai>VADER</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>* DARTH VADER</pattern>
    <template><srai>VADER</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>* SKYWALKER</pattern>
    <template><srai>VADER</srai></template>
  </category>
  <category>
    <pattern>SKYWALKER *</pattern>
